Description





  Sanchar Saathi is a citizen centric initiative of Department of Telecommunications (DoT) to empower mobile subscribers, strengthen their security and increase awareness about citizen centric initiatives of the Government. Sanchar Saathi is available in form of Mobile App and web portal (www.sancharsaathi.gov.in).  Sanchar Saathi provides various citizen centric services as follows:
1. Chakshu - Report Suspected Fraud Communication
2. Block Your Lost/ Stolen Mobile Handset
3. Know Mobile Connections in Your Name
4. Know genuineness of Your Mobile Handset
5. Report Incoming International Call with Indian Number






